description:

  • 1 Year on Refrigerator and 10 Years on Compressor

Product description

From the Manufacturer

6th Sense Activefresh

With the revolutionary 6th Sense ActiveFresh Technology, presenting the 3 door Protton World Series Refrigerator. Its Active Fresh Zone with Moisture Retention and the incredible MicroBlock, keeps your fruits and vegetables fresher for longer.

  • Moisture Retention Technology
  • Microblock
  • Fresh Keeper
  • Air Boosters
  • 3 Door Format
Fresh Keeper

Keeps Vegetables fresh for long time.

AIRBOOSTERS

The new Airbooster system controls the circulation the cold air, so that each compartment receives the precise cooling it requires. This not only provides the most efficient cooling of each section but also prevents odor mixing between the three zones.

MOISTURE RETENTION

In ordinary refrigerators, the cold air comes directly in contact with fruits and vegetables and robs them of their intrinsic moisture. But in Proton World series refrigerator, the cold air flows around the compartment, keeping the contents cool while retaining their moisture and natural freshness.

MICROBLOCK

Micro-block is a special anti-microbial additive that is present in the material of the compartment itself, which kills up to 99.9 percent of microbes and provides lifelong protection against contamination.

name: LG 258 L 4 Star Frost-Free Double Door Refrigerator (GL-D292JMFL, Marine Florid)
description:
• Frost-free double-door refrigerator; 258 litres capacity
  • Energy Rating: 4 Star
  • LG's new smart inverter compressor is one of the most advanced and energy efficient compressor that saves energy upto 36 percent by adjusting cooling power in response to the amount of food you load in the refrigerator which provides efficient energy consumption
  • This is a special lattice-type box cover which maintains moisture at an optimum level
  • Top LED: LG's unique top LED provides you premium looks, uniform brightness across the refrigerator

Product description

Product Description

Refrigerator with Advanced Technology from LG

If you are looking for a Refrigerator which is high on performance and less on energy consumption then buy the LG GL-D292JMFL Frost-free Double-door Refrigerator from Amazon India. The Refrigerator has a capacity of 258 litres and the Energy Rating is 3 stars. It comes with 1 Year warranty on product; 10 year warranty on compressor. It is available in Marine Florid colour.

Maintains Moisture at an Optimum Level: The new Convertible Box in this Refrigerator gives you the option of either keeping fresh fruits/Vegetables etc by adjusting the lever to left side or store non vegetarian item by moving the lever to right side. The temperature control for this box works between -1 to 4 degrees centigrade. The Three - star energy rating refrigerator comes with a built- in setting that includes the special lattice- type box cover that maintains the moisture at an optimal level. The moisture from foods evaporates and condenses on the lattice, thus maintaining the correct balance of moisture in the box. The Ice Beam Door Cooling ensures even circulation from vents along the back of the Fridge. The UltraCool Gel material preinstalled in the freezer ensures that food stays fresh up to 10 hours in case of power cut. The Refrigerator comes with a double twist ice tray. The Refrigerator can store up to 2 litres bottle.

Innovative Features: The LG GL-D292JMFL Frost-free Double-door is equipped with New Smart Inverter Compressor which can adjust the cooling requirement as per the food item stored in Fridge and thus saves energy up to 36percent. LG as manufactures are committed to making products with lesser carbon emission. The Refrigerator comes with long lasting Top LED for uniform brightness across. The Refrigerator comes with Smart connect inverter and can be plugged into Home inverter for backup power in case of power cut. During Power cut it would consume power less than 2 CFL bulbs. It works without a stabilizer and is built to withstand a fluctuation ranging from 100 Volts to 290 Volts.

Installation: Once you buy the product from Amazon India you can call LG support on 18003159999 directly for installation/Demo. Don’t forget to mention the model name of the unit to the LG support.

From the Manufacturer

Smart Inverter Compressor

LG's New Smart Inverter Compressor is one of the most advanced and energy efficient compressor that saves energy upto 36%* by adjusting cooling power in response to the amount of food you load in the refrigerator which provides efficient energy consumption. Designed to give you unmatched performance, great savings and super silent operation, the New Smart Inverter Compressor is yet another delightful innovation for your convenience.


Smart Diagnosis

Fast and Effective diagnosis for problems.


Cool Refrigerator

The LG Refrigerator initiative focuses on environmentally sustainable solutions through Eco-Design and Eco-Products, reduction of hazardous materials and addressing global climate change like Global Warming.Our product emits less carbon and don't harm the Ozone layer, so that we've a greener tomorrow!


Convertible Box

Convertible BoxA separate compartment which keeps your food fresh and healthy where you can control the temperature of Veg or Non-Veg items by adjusting the lever to the left side for fresh fruits and vegetables and right side for non veg items Storage (Temp Range is -1 Deg C to 4 Deg C).


MOIST BALANCE CRISPER

This is a special lattice-type box cover which maintains moisture at an optimum level. Moisture from stored food is evaporated and then condensed on the lattice, maintaining the correct balance of moisture in the box.


Tower LED

Brighter, durable, cooler and energy efficient light. And you contribute to a greener planet for years.


Ever Fresh Zone

A special large fresh zone with Moist Balance Crisper and Humidity Controller that keeps vegetables fresh.


Beauty & Care

Now your refrigerator gives you a separate corner to store all your medical and beauty products. Preserve their goodness and give them a touch of freshness with this unique feature.


Double Twist Ice Tray

Allow you to get extra ice when you need some extra.


Power Cut Evercool

The Temperature of the refrigerator is maintained and the freshness of food is preserved upto 7 hours in the refrigerator section and upto 10 hours in the freezer section.


DURACHILL

LG Dura Chill maintains optimum cooling inside the refrigerator for up to 10 hrs*, even during power cuts. Developed with a special gel material, it minimizes loss of cooling and prevents food items from getting spoilt. Also, its unique placement on the freezer top provides uniform cooling with a ‘shower’ effect. *Under standard LGEIL Test Conditions.

From the Manufacturer

Smart Inverter Compressor

LG's New Smart Inverter Compressor is one of the most advanced and energy efficient compressor that saves energy upto 36%* by adjusting cooling power in response to the amount of food you load in the refrigerator which provides efficient energy consumption. Designed to give you unmatched performance, great savings and super silent operation, the New Smart Inverter Compressor is yet another delightful innovation for your convenience.

Multi Air Flow

LG's Multi Air Flow ensures even cooling by dispersing Cool air effectively in multiple directions throughout the refrigerator by using the multi flow air vents located all over the refrigerator. Thus helps in keeping the food fresh & healthy.

Friendly Refrigerator

The LG initiative focuses on environmentally sustainable solutions through Eco-Design and Eco-Products, reduction of hazardous materials and addressing global climate change like Global Warming.Our product emits less carbon and don't harm the Ozone layer, so that we've a greener tomorrow!.

Pull Out Tray

Specially Designed tray to store frequently used items.

MOIST BALANCE CRISPER

This is a special lattice-type box cover which maintains moisture at an optimum level. Moisture from stored food is evaporated and then condensed on the lattice, maintaining the correct balance of moisture in the box.

Top LED

LG’s Unique Top LED Provides you Premium Looks, Uniform brightness across the refrigerator, better Interior Aesthetics, Durability & Energy Efficiency.

Ever Fresh Zone

A special large fresh zone with Moist Balance Crisper and Humidity Controller that keeps vegetables fresh.

Moveable Twist Ice Tray

You can now adjust the Ice Tray as per your convenience and need.
